title: Tom Palmer - Free Trade, Protectionism, GM, and Peter Schiff Part 1/3
description: Tom Palmer, Senior Fellow of Cato, and head of the Atlas Economic Research Foundation chats with Austin Petersen of the Libertarian Party. In this video he discusses the economic implications of the collapse of General Motors, protectionism under Obama, his recent back and forth with Peter Schiff on Freedom Watch, and the goal of Atlas.
